{"tid":2143521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"郵局條龍長過投注站，點解唔開番六合彩","createTime":"2020-08-07T06:47:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T15:47:27.000Z","uid":24730,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e20d497bc0a98fb6aa883a56a5387741db5ac120","tid":2143521,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T06:47:56.000Z","msg":"郵局日日排長龍，但投注站就話驚多人排隊唔開得，連帶六合彩都停咗半年。<br />\n<br />\n喂大佬，點解郵局開得，投注站唔開得。喺而家乜撚都唔畀做嘅時候，恢復六合彩畀人發下夢麻醉下都好吖。如果驚太多人排隊，點解唔趁而家鼓勵多啲人開網上戶口投注？"},{"pid":"22df03f5951e10f07d85072ec614f8bfe3cb9cd6","tid":2143521,"uid":307927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T06:50:28.000Z","msg":"馬會呢排都周轉不靈<br />\n無多餘錢潑出去做六合彩獎金"},{"pid":"16942b7b240c05bd79d010243d4a64dcb8f190dc","tid":2143521,"uid":11067,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"22df03f5951e10f07d85072ec614f8bfe3cb9cd6","tid":2143521,"uid":307927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T06:50:28.000Z","msg":"馬會呢排都周轉不靈<br />\n無多餘錢潑出去做六合彩獎金"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T06:52:44.000Z","msg":"開個一億金多寶 三四億投注額<br />\n之後頭獎無人中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e80d5c4f94b2ed778771f54f94e02787e14e605a","tid":2143521,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T07:16:15.000Z","msg":"又話舞照跳、馬照跑"},{"pid":"50280d44f76582cd8bb130be5ebcb215bb1c4af5","tid":2143521,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e80d5c4f94b2ed778771f54f94e02787e14e605a","tid":2143521,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T07:16:15.000Z","msg":"又話舞照跳、馬照跑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T07:17:11.000Z","msg":"所以之前有馬跑<br />\n但無話六合彩照攪"},{"pid":"bc674effd87731a7a5e31c06f678537db721b069","tid":2143521,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T07:19:57.000Z","msg":"[賽馬會] 衰啲講句，做咩唔發行刮刮樂<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2127406\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\"